Special thanks to #ebooks on irchighway, where you can find all of these ebooks in their original lit, epub, html, rtf, txt or whatever format.

I converted these to MOBI for my own personal ease of use. There wasn't any consolidated Shadowrun novel collection for mobi, and as far as I can tell, this is the most complete collection on the web thus far.

This is a gift to the Shadowrun community, without whose support the two highly anticipated PC games, Shadowrun Returns and Shadowrun Online, wouldn't exist (not to mention the resurgence in popularity of the PnP supplements).

Much gratitude to all Kickstarter backers and, of course, all the great men and ladies that continue to work tirelessly to make Shadowrun a fantastic universe for us to &quot;live&quot; and play in.

